genresAdvancedInfo.name: whale song
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Whale song is a type of music that features the sounds of whales singing and communicating with each other. It is often used in meditation and relaxation practices due to its calming and soothing nature. The songs are created by recording the sounds of whales in their natural habitat and then manipulating them to create a musical composition.
